</section>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    background: #fafafa;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 .75rem;
  }
  .page-hero p {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>


    <main>
      <section class="about">
        <!-- Row 1 -->
        <div class="row">
          <img src="/JHY .png" alt="Introducing Joseph Yim" class="photo" />
          <div class="copy">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <h2>Bio</h2>
            <p>
              testing testing . blah blah Every story deserves to be told clearly and authentically.
              We help students refine their ideas into personal narratives that stand out to admissions committees.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Row 2 (flipped on desktop) -->
        <div class="row row-reverse">
          <div class="copy">
            <h2>testing 1</h2>
            <p>
              From brainstorming to final polish, our editors work closely with each student to
              uncover their strongest themes and deliver essays that capture who they are.
            </p>
          </div>
          <img src="/KYM.png" alt="Introducing Kristine Ma" class="photo" />
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <style>
      .about {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
      }
      .row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
      }
      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .row { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
        .row-reverse { direction: rtl; }
        .row-reverse > * { direction: ltr; }
      }
      .photo {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        display: block;
      }
      .copy h1 { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; }
      .copy h2 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; }
      .copy p { color: #555; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
